						               													<description>&amp;quot;The Army Lists in this booklet have primarily been compiled for use with the Fast Play Ancient Warfare Rules published by Newbury Rules. They may also be used in conjunction with other rules including our own 'Warfare in the Ancient World', though some amendment of the troop descriptions and figure points values will be required. The novel format of the Lists is designed to enable the player to devise his model army quickly and simply whilst ensuring a realistic balance of the component troop types, this is of course in keeping with the concept of the Fast Play Rules themselves.&amp;quot; - Ancient Warfare Army Lists suitable for Fast Play Rules &amp;amp; Big Battles, R. G. Boss &amp;amp; T. J. Halsall, Newbury Rules, 1985, p.1&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Additional section (pages 35-36) on converting these lists for other rules, in particular WRG War Games Rules 3000 BC to 1485 AD, 6th Edition.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
